===============
MapReduce++v2.1
---------------

API based on vectors.

===============
MapReduce++v2.0
---------------

The MapReduce++v2.0 integrates the corresponding second versions of MaPI and MapMP MapReduce implementations. 
The main factor that justify the jump from 1.x to the 2.x versions is the using of MapReduce Interface (MRI),
which was proposed by the MaPI developments in order to make easily its comprehension and using by the users.

See our examples!
:)
